    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relic Delivery </strong>is an action roguelike where you shoot lots of enemies following your truck, which is initially armed with just a machine gun. As the enemies get more and more aggressive, you must use the power from the stolen Time Relic you are carrying to aid your escape. The power that the relic grants you not only makes you more powerful but also changes the reality you perceive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293650/extras/4fdba233b81d00d7f794840f6a804a76.poster.avif?t=1731473930\" width=616 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293650/extras/4fdba233b81d00d7f794840f6a804a76.webm?t=1731473930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293650/extras/4fdba233b81d00d7f794840f6a804a76.mp4?t=1731473930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Notice: <strong>Relic Delivery</strong> is still in its very early stage, the features here either are incomplete or subject to change.</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric convoy vibe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reality-bending upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and satisfying control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting meta-progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many game modes</p></li></ul>",
